text: Bryukhovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Bryukhovskoye Rural Settlement, Yelovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 377 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 18 km SSW from Yelovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yelovsky District
title: Bryukhovo
